<item>
            <title>[LU-7013] replay-single test_110c: FAIL: create striped dir failed </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7013</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While verifying patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/14912&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/14912&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6556&quot; title=&quot;changelog catalog corruption if all possible records is define &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6556&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6556&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; on master branch with DNE configuration, replay-single test_110c failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;shadow-16vm9: CMD: shadow-16vm9.shadow.whamcloud.com lctl get_param -n at_max
shadow-16vm10: CMD: shadow-16vm10.shadow.whamcloud.com lctl get_param -n at_max
shadow-16vm9: mdc.lustre-MDT0001-mdc-*.mds_server_uuid in FULL state after 4 sec
shadow-16vm10: mdc.lustre-MDT0001-mdc-*.mds_server_uuid in FULL state after 4 sec
Can&apos;t lstat /mnt/lustre/d110c.replay-single/striped_dir: No such file or directory
 replay-single test_110c: @@@@@@ FAIL: create striped dir failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;replay-single test 110{d,e,g} also failed with the same failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maloo report: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/1a8282a6-43d8-11e5-a4bc-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/1a8282a6-43d8-11e5-a4bc-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By searching on Maloo, I found the failure was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/13786&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/13786&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3534&quot; title=&quot;async update cross-MDTs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3534&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3534&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ee143472-ee18-11e4-848f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ee143472-ee18-11e4-848f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre Branch: master&lt;br/&gt;
